Male: Body length 9.0 mm, forewing length 12.0 mm, forewing width 3.8 mm, forewing and hindwing with sporadically arranged circular pale spots, length of each antenna 17.0 mm. Body, antennae, palpi, and wings yellowish brown, abdomen brown with black spots, legs and genitalia yellowish brown (
Figs 8–9
).

