Female genitalia (
Fig. 7
): Simple, of medium length. Segments VIII and IX with setose tergum and sternum. Segment IX roughly trapezoidal in lateral view. Segment XI with dorsal apodemes extending anteriorly into segment VII. Segment X with basal apodemes also extending anteriorly into segment VII. Basal apodemes with short subapicodorsal point. Segment XI with pair of terminal papillae and pair of cerci.
